  title="Image Compression Formats Compared: JPG vs WebP vs AVIF in 2026"
  description="Which format gives the best quality at the smallest file size? A practical comparison of JPG, WebP, and AVIF with real-world data and browser support numbers for 2026."
  publishDate="2026-05-23"
